{"tid":216491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"借錢救命，求巴打們入一入幫手","createTime":"2017-04-25T08:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T14:05:17.000Z","uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d45520a15b4b65b0caed619f7c1a789b904913e2","tid":216491,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"小弟最近想借75000蚊去找哂d舊數，但我呢幾萬蚊都係呢半年內借，個tu評級可能有啲低，頭先問左安信佢話我唔夠評級唔肯借，想問下巴打們有無咩意見同推薦邊到借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下留反我借錢嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月 - ua借左10000加5千備用現金<br />\n2017年1月 - 邦民借左10000<br />\n2017年2月 - ua借左5000<br />\n2017年3月-邦民借左30000，找左1月借嗰10000，當時實拎22000<br />\n2017年3月尾 - ua借左12000<br />\n<br />\n早兩日計過條數d息口好貴，同而家手頭好緊想借多幾千週轉下，巴打們有無意見可以比下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：不是賭錢欠債，以前係外地讀書出左事，要賠幾萬蚊，當時借左身邊朋友好多錢，呢d錢係借黎還比朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeec5cc668c6f25f3e4bc42e8b516a5499dd5cd0","tid":216491,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"借黎還比朋友 是咪on9<br />\n屋企人呢？做緊乜？月入？<br />\n咪撚借了 愈大條數愈撚衰"},{"pid":"a8db002b198320aed31669582077619250a2d580","tid":216491,"uid":50122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"賣屎忽"},{"pid":"17ea9e6482b642b9976784ac41109d0f0a6b5c7c","tid":216491,"uid":30604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"一月仲話去北海道 三月仲話出兩部iPhone 7 都係算鳩數啦 此post已完"},