 />\n屋企人唔知呢件事，同我自己搞出黎想自己解決返，我可以慢慢還，只係唔想捱貴息，見有d卡數一筆清嘅product，想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9db9a7f194eb23b4ae1d8a750db64cd93c2e577","tid":216491,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一月仲話去北海道 三月仲話出兩部iPhone 7 都係算鳩數啦 此post已完</blockquote><br />\n1月去旅行係我屋企人請我去grad trip ，iphone係幫朋友問，我都係好聲好氣想問下意見，巴打唔使咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解差咁多錢都去到北海道 即係屋企人有錢啦 咁借黎做乜9"},{"pid":"4b744a62c0f5ea2261999a127c710b2e471a05de","tid":216491,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"搵定地方跳樓啦"},{"pid":"53266987ae638e2fe08ae3edf377a5ce0a4b5baf","tid":216491,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"借屋企人錢好過借財仔啦 訓撚醒未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f3f20a8ec6efc6b6cb57e69d89983eee7b2cf4","tid":216491,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一月仲話去北海道 三月仲話出兩部iPhone 7 都係算鳩數啦 此post已完</blockquote><br />\n1月去旅行係我屋企人請我去grad trip ，iphone係幫朋友問，我都係好聲好氣想問下意見，巴打唔使咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解差咁多錢都去到北海道 即係屋企人有錢啦 咁借黎做乜9</blockquote><br />\n屋企人唔知呢件事，我想自己私下了左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbafa3fd9fc0d29a249039fdbe06902cb6f820b9","tid":216491,"uid":74281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"低能仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e965d22c8d1bb22c5593a7b03298fd1d9fea8fff","tid":216491,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>低能仔<img src=\"/asset